## 💾 Installation

VSCodeVim can be installed via the VS Code [Marketplace](https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=vscodevim.vim) or the OpenVSX [Marketplace](https://open-vsx.org/extension/vscodevim/vim).

### Mac

